Support Timing Data

Data from the Support Timing Study

This study was referred to as the “Before/After” study by the project team, as the principle conditions were supports before or supports after the levels.

The data are available in the following file:

Timing Support Data (CSV format)

Metadata are available using the readr cols format in this R metadata Before/After script.

The following steps will load the file using the metadata in R.

library(readr)
source("https://pluto.coe.fsu.edu/PhysicsDataPlayground/Data/BAMetadata.R")
PPIESBAdata <- 
  read_csv("https://pluto.coe.fsu.edu/PhysicsDataPlayground/Data/BAdata.csv",
           col_types=colBAdata)

IDs and Study Conditions

  • UID, uid.x, uid.y – Subject idenfiers identical except for three missing values.
  • Source, Cohort – The sample from which the subject was drawn: Values are After School, DCSD, FSUS, HCR, Summer Camp
  • Consent, Assent – 1 if assent from student and consent from parents was received. (Note, all records with 0’s in either column were removed.)
  • Condition
  • CounterBalance
  • Pre_Form, Post_Form

Demographic Variables

  • Age
  • Sex
  • Ethnicity
  • Gaming
  • Physics

Pretest/Posttest

  • Pre_Dur, Post_Dur
  • Pre_Near, Post_Near
  • Pre_Far, Post_Far
  • Pre_Total, Post_Total
  • Gain, Gain_Near, Gain_Far

IMI Questionnaire

  • Enjoy
  • Competence
  • Effort
  • Frustation, LackOfFrustration – Frustration and reversed Frustration scale.
  • Value
  • Survey_Missing – 1 for (3) student who did not respond to IMI questionnaire

  • Pretest Near Transfer ECT: pre_NQ1_ect.lever, pre_NQ2_ect.lever, pre_NQ3_ect.pendulum, pre_NQ4_ect.pendulum, pre_NQ5_ect.ramp, pre_NQ6_ect.ramp, pre_NQ7_ect.springboard, pre_NQ8_ect.springboard

  • Pretest Far Transfer ECT: pre_FQ1_ect.lever, pre_FQ2_ect.lever, pre_FQ3_ect.pendulum, pre_FQ4_ect.pendulum, pre_FQ5_ect.ramp, pre_FQ6_ect.ramp, pre_FQ7_ect.springboard, pre_FQ8_ect.springboard

  • Pretest Far Transfer POT: pre_FQ9_pot.lever.distance, pre_FQ10_pot.lever.distance, pre_FQ11_pot.lever.mass, pre_FQ12_pot.lever.mass, pre_FQ13_pot.springboard, pre_FQ14_pot.springboard
